'''Meshack Mavuso Magabane''' (yavutse ku ya 8 Mata 1977), ni umukinnyi wa filime akaba n'umuyobozi wa filimi muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] . Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri seri izwi cyane ''Heist'', ''Isidingo'', ''Yizo Yizo'', Isithembiso na Durban gen. <ref name="savannanews">https://savannanews.com/meshack-mavuso-biography-age-wife-children-debt-tv-roles-net-worth-durban-gen/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 8 Mata 1977 i Mandagsoek Limpopo, muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]. <ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2bca4226af</ref> Arubatse, ni se w'abana bane.

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1998 yakoze umwanya wa mbere 'Vusi Moletsane' mu ikinamico  ''Isidingo'' yamenyekanye cyane. <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2018-03-26-meshack-mavuso-on-being-broke-id-go-to-the-bathroom--cry/</ref> Hanyuma, yagaragaye mu ikinamico ''Yizo Yizo'' yerekanwe kuva 1999 kugeza 2004 afite uruhare 'Jabulani "Javas" Nyembe'. <ref>https://www.power987.co.za/featured/listen-yizo-yizo-made-meshack-mavusos-acting-career/</ref>

Yamenyekanye kandi ubwo yinjiraga muri Mzansi Magic telenovela Isithembiso yerekanwe bwa mbere ku ya 3 Mata 2017, aho yakinnye imico ya Keromemang Mtimande, se wa Tshepo, wabitswe na se na nyina kugeza igihe yavumbuwe mu buryo butangaje. gira umwana numukunzi we Chlodea ubu bakundana numwanzi we.

Yatangiye umwuga we nka Meshack Mavuso akina 'Simiso Mtshali' mu gice cya kabiri n'icya gatatu cy'urukurikirane rw'abapolisi ''Zero Tolerance'' yerekanwe muri SABC2. Mbere yizo nshingano zashimwe cyane, yakinnye imico itandukanye  mu gice cya mbere. Mu mwaka wa 2008, yari umwe mu babyinnyi b'ibyamamare mu Kubyina umwaka mushya , ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2008. 

Muri 2009, yagaragaye ashyigikiwe nigihembwe cyambere cyuruhererekane rwerekana ibisekuruza ''Who Do You Think You Are?'' cyari gishingiye ku ruhererekane rw'Abongereza . Urukurikirane rwaciye kuri SABC2 muri 2009. Muri 2014, yagarutse kuri tereviziyo akina visits mu bice bibiri by'ikinamico ya Sida ''City'' yakinnye nka 'dogiteri'. Muri 2015, ku nshuro ya mbere, yakoresheje izina Mavuso Magabane mri seri ''Zabalaza'' . Muri seri, yakinnye Visits mugice kimwe. Muri 2016 yakoze umwanya wa kabiri ayoboye muri e.tv ikinamico  ''Heist'' hamwe ninshingano ya 'Chairman'. 

Muri 2020 nyuma yigihe gito muri serial ''The River'', yinjiye mu bakinnyi ba serial ''Durban Gen'' aho akina imico ya Dr Thabo Dlamini ugaragara nkumugore kandi akaba yarashakanye na Dr Precious Dlamini. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/news/meshack-mavuso-on-starring-in-durban-gen-and-lessons-hes-learnt-in-his-career-20200930</ref>

